data.description: Impressive 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom POOL home with attached 2 Car Garage located in the desirable "New York" section of Port Charlotte. NO HOA. This home was beautifully upgraded in 2022 : Kitchen, Bathrooms, flooring, **NEW ROOF Aug 2022** (no damage to roof in hurricane Ian). This light and bright home offers an open and split bedroom floor plan with Living Room/ Dining Room, well appointed Kitchen. The Living Room with large window offering lots of natural light opens to the Dining Room. The remodeled Kitchen features new white cabinetry, stainless appliances including a gas stove, granite counters and backsplash, good counter and cabinet space. The attached Garage offers the laundry, pull down opening to attic, side door, garage door opener, freezer. The spacious Master Bedroom suite has a walk in closet and private bathroom with walk in shower. There are two additional good sized bedrooms and the guest bathroom has a large walk in shower. Your living space extends via sliding glass doors to the screened lanai with inground heated fiberglass pool, covered lanai and plenty of deck for sunbathing. Pool heater is one year old. Private garden view of lovely Florida friendly landscaping. The yard is completely fenced with a chain link fence- perfect for your family and pets. Other features include screened front entry, rain gutters, hurricane shutters, wood look tile floors throughout the home, all new six panel doors (one year) , all new light fixtures (one year), awning on lanai, some soffits and gutters are new. Some furniture will convey if the buyer wants it. Propane tank for gas stove is rented. This home is located in the heart of Port Charlotte minutes from shopping, dining, medical care, waterfront parks, fishing piers, boat ramps, Port Charlotte Beach Complex.  Perfect for year round living and for those expecting lots of winter visitors!
